## 3.0.0

### Architecture
[Change] Universal agent architecture — 6 domain-agnostic agents replace
         12 domain-specific agents
[Change] Governance initialization model — project data drives agent behavior
[Change] /r- command namespace — 13 lifecycle + 10 utility commands
[Change] Profiles become governance seed templates, not agent bundles
[Change] CC agent name prefix rfxn- -> rdf-
[Remove] Domain-prefixed agents (sys-eng, fe-qa, sec-eng, etc.)
[Remove] ~45 domain-specific slash commands
[Remove] profile.json manifest files

### Agents
[New] planner — research-driven collaborative planning (opus)
[New] dispatcher — plan execution orchestrator (sonnet)
[New] engineer — universal implementation engineer (opus)
[New] qa — verification gate (sonnet)
[New] uat — user acceptance testing (sonnet)
[New] reviewer — adversarial review, challenge + sentinel modes (opus)

### Lifecycle Commands
[New] /r-init — governance initialization
[New] /r-start — session initialization with context anchor
[New] /r-plan — 5-phase planner workflow
