[New] /r-refresh — governance-aware codebase re-scan
[New] /r-sync — canonical source pull-back
[New] /r-audit — full codebase audit with parallel dispatch
[New] /r-ship — composite release workflow
[New] /build — plan phase execution via dispatcher
[New] /verify — QA verification via qa subagent
[New] /test — UAT acceptance via uat subagent
[New] /review — adversarial review in challenge or sentinel mode

### Utility Commands
